		<title>【共产主义的终极目的】之十九：打开地狱门</title>
		<link>https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/19/4/23/n11206376.htm</link>
		<pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2019 16:43:59 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[各地分网]]></category>
