		<title>【共产主义的终极目的】之六：甜头和苦头</title>
		<link>https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/19/3/7/n11096971.htm</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 28 Feb 2019 14:08:37 +0000</pubDate>
